JoinRequestDialog.title: Kobatok ilo ruum eo .
JoinRequestDialog.inviteOnly: Eñin ej juon ruum̦ make im ej aikuj wõr peba in kũr ko ñan kobal̦o̦k .
JoinRequestDialog.knockRequired: Ruum in ej aikuj kōjerbale n̄an kobaļo̧k. Klik ilo button eo ñan jilkinḷọk kajjitōk eo ñan kōṃṃane .
JoinRequestDialog.canJoin: Eñin ej juon ruum̧ in armej, kwomaroñ kobatok ilo jim̧we .

MessageList.noMessages: Ejjeļo̧k ennaan kiiō, jilkinļo̧k ennaan eo m̧oktata n̄an jino bwebwenato eo!
MessageList.historyEnd: Eṃōj an itok nuuj eo ṃoktata .
